Tania Fédor https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tania_F%C3%A9dor 0 Tania Fédor (3 November 1905 – 1 December 1985) was a Monaco-born French film actress who played a number of leading roles during the 1930s and early 1940s in films such as Fantômas (1932). She later settled in Canada and worked on French language productions there.
